name: Jared Dickson
body:
### Currrent State

I'm working in AngularJS and WebAPI development using Onion Architecture. @rivardja has been getting me up to speed on best practice and development patterns. Another member of the team I'm collaborating with is @LeeFlannery.

### Development Interests

Projects that grab my intention generally reside in the realms of mobile apps, user privacy and information security. I've done projects in native mobile, as well as @xamarin and @phonegap.

### Contact

You can follow me on Twitter via [@kraihn](https://www.twitter.com/kraihn) or check out my profile on [LinkedIn](https://www.linkedin.com/in/kraihn).
